While staying at Sunflower Two Hotel, visitors can check out Cannon Fort (0.2 mi), which is a popular Cat Ba attraction. As your “home away from home,” the small hotel rooms offer a refrigerator and air conditioning, and getting online is easy, with free internet access available. Guests have access to room service while staying at Sunflower Two Hotel. In addition, Sunflower Two Hotel offers an on-site restaurant, which will help make your Cat Ba trip additionally gratifying. If you’re looking for a Spanish restaurant, consider a visit to LoHi Sky Lounge, which is not far from Sunflower Two Hotel. Sunflower Two Hotel puts the best of Cat Ba at your fingertips, making your stay both relaxing and enjoyable.
